    "updated_at": "2025-03-14T21:21:02Z",
    "body": "I think it's in the repositories for Debian `trixie`. I was unable to get the `cargo install` to work on Ubuntu `noble` in 2 GB of RAM on the BeagleV Fire. The path of least resistance is just to wait for `trixie` to go stable. (Or set up a cross-build toolchain on an x86_64 box with plenty of CPU and RAM; it's a massive build job.)",
